{"tid":2075530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮：中美貿易協議已經「玩完」","createTime":"2020-06-23T02:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T04:13:33.000Z","uid":7542,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4a6c5eb49f7cf98b865e3f0decf38eb9c721c329","tid":2075530,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:07:43.000Z","msg":"美國白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅表示，中美貿易協議已經「完結」。納瓦羅接受霍士新聞訪問時表示，中美貿易協議的轉捩點在於中方延誤通報疫情。納瓦羅指，美中雙方在今年1月15日簽署貿易協議後，美方才知道疫情擴散情況。中美過去先後就疫情、香港等事務問題上導致關係緊張。美國總統特朗普日前認為，自己達成一份非常好的協議，中方正購買很多美國貨，可能會購買總值2500億美元的美國商品。他又承認，推遲制裁打壓新疆維吾爾人的中國官員，是為了避免影響中美貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533560-20200623.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533560-20200623.htm&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=6f363944\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533560-20200623.htm&h=55eb0785\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533560-20200623.htm</a>"},{"pid":"88e581f3e586a340a202ce2a57dbe61b933ca5b0","tid":2075530,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:08:30.000Z","msg":"唔洗急，最緊要快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d534e72cf149aed50f7cc580af2938d5a954b9d7","tid":2075530,"uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"唔知大家係咪都對本土知識頻道冇乜興趣，如果可以嘅希望大家都抽時間支持一下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其是係同我哋息息相關嘅議題：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0ggBftnYDQ4&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=fb7c12ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4</a>"},{"pid":"ac4ce165f312d3995f813fe38e718d8c23dd1973","tid":2075530,"uid":5421,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTi